    "Next, RNNs progress to the fully-connected layer, consolidating the knowledge into the decision-making process Fig. 2 Visualization of CNN sample based on the reference of [14] which involves tasks including prediction and classification.",
    "Finally, RNNs employ the Softmax function, which assigns a probability score to each possible outcome.The potential of RNNs extends even further as researchers continually explore ways to enhance their capabilities.",
